e":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本<del>野</del>最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同"},{"pid":"7a174de9b36537b3abed4034d1ea1185f00bb451","tid":359041,"uid":33535,"like":69,"dislike":5,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本<del>野</del>最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n點都好過D門面野又唔做又冇內涵呀"},{"pid":"f42392fd96a45905a2863b1af15b5bfd4d7d4d2e","tid":359041,"uid":65144,"like":84,"dislike":3,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本<del>野</del>最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n睇到你呢句就知你係唔識煮野食d傻閪"},{"pid":"9580c5da7a27bed0f16645d5b157acfcf1e7e80d","tid":359041,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"佢地係咪唔會叮飯就咁凍食？<br />\n見親啲飯盒都唔放得入微波爐"},{"pid":"99a43fac4fc90a1acff2f831bf1831b373118e4f","tid":359041,"uid":66759,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"8e8ad380bd83573b5e6edb0db80dc05d4d1cbcd0","tid":359041,"uid":65931,"like":33,"dislike":68,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日本<del>野</del>最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n睇到你呢句就知你係唔識煮野食d傻閪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就傻閪<br />\n睇你個樣就知你係冇內涵既小學雞<br />\n<br />\n日本整到個便當比仔比老公呢種文化<br />\n背後係藏住一種好ON9既競爭<br />\n為左可以令老公同仔女係同事or同學面前炫耀<br />\n死整爛整一D可愛但唔包肚既野<br />\n如果你唔整或整得樣衰<br />\n就比人背後話你老婆料理唔得<br />\n<br />\n整又死唔整又死<br />\n好多日本主婦會為左咁去上一D整便當既課程<br />\n為既只係令自己屋企人有面子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5ce92069dc94f628be93599e96bd610d799f14","tid":359041,"uid":37719,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/hS4kAQ/P_20170721_001749.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2FhS4kAQ%2FP_20170721_001749.jpg&h=0bee17f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/dYVLc5/P_20170721_002353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2FdYVLc5%2FP_20170721_002353.jpg&h=45c90598&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f92d12ebeb52794cd38ec47fef779369b4f809ff","tid":359041,"uid":30678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"凍嘅"},{"pid":"80d267d02ce610931b9d40e274cb3719a78783f0","tid":359041,"uid":12628,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"日本嘅主婦會每日為外出返工返學嘅家人整家便當，果種愛心同高超廚藝，真係令人羨慕不已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反觀港女...唔踢你落床叫你買埋早餐比佢食已經好賢慧"},{"pid":"a975b59e51c787fb649c2eacd8dbd6400fc7a67a","tid":359041,"uid":3146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"想學 邊度有得學<br />\n利申：識煮飯 但整公仔唔掂"},{"pid":"93cb2deb91e8cfacbdf316028642e30b278bdce2","tid":359041,"uid":126305,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/hS4kAQ/P_20170721_001749.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2FhS4kAQ%2FP_20170721_001749.jpg&h=0bee17f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/dYVLc5/P_20170721_002353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2FdYVLc5%2FP_20170721_002353.jpg&h=45c90598&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712f258be95dbc6d29ace61adf4db59d119e30bb","tid":359041,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:14:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5301bf0ef8be78c3272b54b657c2b6491b12cc6","tid":359041,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/hS4kAQ/P_20170721_001749.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2FhS4kAQ%2FP_20170721_001749.jpg&h=0bee17f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.ibb.co/dYVLc5/P_20170721_002353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.ibb.co%2FdYVLc5%2FP_20170721_002353.jpg&h=45c90598&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一冇左個樣變狗飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe61e24251ca4c5aff458ba8ced3b7dcd9ada2d","tid":359041,"uid":21514,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本野最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n機場d手信包到靚一靚<br />\n但9成都好難食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/084439_bff4163c522cebcbd02560b90714f825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F084439_bff4163c522cebcbd02560b90714f825.jpg&h=0c9be4ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90779e3f35214f2061397ca9abcd7e1727967643","tid":359041,"uid":137647,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:49:48.000Z","msg":"同過日本人一齊，食就可能唔一定好食，但見到佢整到個飯盒又精緻又靚，食落感覺係唔同d。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果港女學左真係有機會一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識得既港女都識煮下野食<br />\n只係唔太想煮/唔想洗野"},{"pid":"4