score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"色香味<br />\n賣相唔可以少"},{"pid":"d600ab6f694d63d346a30438858e4e85c2080aba","tid":359041,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本嘅主婦會每日為外出返工返學嘅家人整家便當，果種愛心同高超廚藝，真係令人羨慕不已<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反觀港女...唔踢你落床叫你買埋早餐比佢食已經好賢慧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔好再講啦"},{"pid":"5f9047a1cf5ca99d90c707630d652b722b02ebd4","tid":359041,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本野最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咬撚死你"},{"pid":"90b90212c07df3f6aaf0fcce5dc7c21ad5d44c2f","tid":359041,"uid":27772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"請看"},{"pid":"0b611d1558d130c0ac2e86e93964c81f665d181f","tid":359041,"uid":65931,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日本<del>野</del>最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n睇到你呢句就知你係唔識煮野食d傻閪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你就傻閪<br />\n睇你個樣就知你係冇內涵既小學雞<br />\n<br />\n日本整到個便當比仔比老公呢種文化<br />\n背後係藏住一種好ON9既競爭<br />\n為左可以令老公同仔女係同事or同學面前炫耀<br />\n死整爛整一D可愛但唔包肚既野<br />\n如果你唔整或整得樣衰<br />\n就比人背後話你老婆料理唔得<br />\n<br />\n整又死唔整又死<br />\n好多日本主婦會為左咁去上一D整便當既課程<br />\n為既只係令自己屋企人有面子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地生活習慣黎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等如你老母新年會煮8個餸<br />\n利申：住過日本年幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咩<br />\n我都住過幾年wor<br />\n整便當 當然係習慣同文化<br />\n但D女人們背後果種比較係幾咁可怕唔知你又睇唔睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7bb129392fea60976aa04533eda2b2b994fa29","tid":359041,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本野最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咬撚死你</blockquote><br />\n等你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3ad18864b6bc6f29ba78e6acaa4cfb16e3609d","tid":359041,"uid":54574,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本野最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咬撚死你</blockquote><br />\n咁所有擺盤同設計都係「XXX最識做係做埋D門面野」"},{"pid":"605240fd5613fb286b3d9e1f81539240b46d2e03","tid":359041,"uid":13521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:31:26.000Z","msg":"有時係度諗<br />\n啲便當好多唔同菜色 要特登整好多但淨係擺一兩舊落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74aa634cacf89c5ad9470099951d3b1877a4839","tid":359041,"uid":137625,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"日本表面睇就好，其實內裡成個民族都係變鳩態痴撚線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390b0a1cd7c13542a7817e3fe83fb0d3680dc2cf","tid":359041,"uid":137625,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日本野最識做係做埋D門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咬撚死你</blockquote><br />\n等你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n迷日狗亂咁吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51e016f675fb5c8314aa4ff9f646c33361b8abc","tid":359041,"uid":22358,"lik