> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到好似香港人唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6bd0f2d454a33913651435836bde8349176caf","tid":359041,"uid":9391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>崇日撚係日本食屎都好味<br />\n根本係日本係無啖好食<br />\n乜乜燒 爛牛 刺身 咖哩 全部都垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9"},{"pid":"3dac4bacb2b74be6c1f3c04240237f8bcf13ded9","tid":359041,"uid":18818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日本表面睇就好，其實內裡成個民族都係變鳩態痴撚線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到好似香港人唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果日本係金肉其外<br />\n咁其他亞洲國家直頭係外內都差啦<br />\n仲好意思批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}